Huge new features accompany this version. Voicerly is by far the most complete and powerful application for audio recordings. Edit mode: With this brand new service merge audio recordings cut or move sections of your recording. Chapters: Cut your audio recording into chapters and start playing from the chapter that interests you. Widgets: With our widgets it has never been so quick and easy to start a recording play a specific recording or add a note to the current recording. Shortcut: With widgets discover new shortcuts that will help you go even faster and automate your tasks. Plus it works with Siri! And much more with more optimized access to your recordings with Spotlight new languages supported by the application or even the use of personal voice.

Big update coming with this version with new features and fixes. Discover annotations a great way to add notes during and after your recordings. We often need to add some ideas or comments but either we do not want disturb the talk or when listening the record. Furthermore these annotations are added to the reports and transcriptions! Add an alert to remember you to stop your record at the time you desire. You can see the time elapsed while recording. App Accessibility gain huge improvements. Summaries and reports was improved for a better result. Minor bugs fixes and performances improvement. Voice Memo Note take a new name for Voicerly. Do not be lost anymore to find our application!
